'''先鋒'''（{{Lang-ru|Авангард}}；{{Lang|en|Vanguard}}；旧称Objekt 4202，Yu-71和Yu-74）是[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]研发的[[高超音速乘波載具|高超音速乘波載具]]（HGV），可以由UR-100UTTKh、R-36M2或RS-28 Sarmat[[重型洲際彈道飛彈|重型洲際彈道飛彈]]作為[[多目標重返大氣層載具|多目標重返大氣層載具]]運載。它既可以運送[[核武器|核武器]]也可以運送[[常規武器|常規武器]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedrive.com/the-war-zone/18906/heres-the-six-super-weapons-putin-unveiled-during-fiery-address|title=Here's The Six Super Weapons Putin Unveiled During Fiery Address|first=Joseph|last=Trevithick|access-date=19 March 2018|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112090339/https://www.thedrive.com/the-war-zone/18906/heres-the-six-super-weapons-putin-unveiled-during-fiery-address|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.defenseworld.net/news/22162#.Wq7Ad0nxJqU|title=Russia's New Avangard Hypersonic Missile System To Enter Service By 2019|website=www.defenseworld.net|access-date=19 March 2018|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111203551/https://www.defenseworld.net/news/22162#.Wq7Ad0nxJqU|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/world/introducing-the-avangard-hypersonic-missile-a-look-inside-putins-new-high-tech-arsenal |title=Introducing 'Avangard' and 'Sarmat': Putin shows off new hypersonic, nuclear missiles |date=1 March 2018 |access-date=19 March 2018}}</ref>。

先锋是[[俄羅斯總統|俄羅斯總統]][[弗拉基米爾·普京|弗拉基米爾·普京]]於2018年3月1日推出的六種新型俄羅斯戰略武器之一。

